dcterms:description: The MSRA10k dataset is the largest publicly available saliency detection dataset, containing 10,000 annotated saliency images used for training a convolutional deconvolutional network to obtain rough saliency maps.
dcterms:title: MSRA10k

dcterms:description: The Street View House Numbers (SVHN) dataset is a real-world image dataset for object recognition, containing 73,257 training digits and 26,032 testing digits, each sized 32 x 32 in RGB color scale.
dcterms:title: Street View House Numbers (SVHN)
